<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
  <div rend="parallel">
     <p xml:id="Aink210-kilavi"> kāppumikutikkaṇ ṭalaimakaṇ melivukaṇṭu teyvattiṉāṉāyiṟṟeṉṟu veṟiyeṭuppuḻit tōḻi cevilik kaṟattoṭu niṉṟatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante standing up with virtue to the foster-mother when the Veṟi-[ritual] was taken up, [when the foster-mother,] observing the weakening of the heroine as guarding increased, [thought] that “it happened because of god.” </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink210">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉainam paṭappaip</l>
<l>pulavuccēr tuṟuka lēṟi yavarnāṭṭup</l>
<l>pūkkeḻu kuṉṟa nōkki niṉṟu</l>
<l>maṇipurai vayaṅkiḻai nilaipeṟat</l>
<l>taṇitaṟku murittava ḷuṟṟa nōyē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
<l>The pain that she experienced too deserves to be alleviated, </l>
<l>so that [she with] glowing jewels resembling sapphires, </l>
<l rend="space indent">who, having ascended the thick stones imbued with the stench of flesh , </l>
<l rend="indent">gazed upon his land’s hill which has flowers, and stood, </l>
<l rend="space">[might] regain [her former] state. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
